&lt;p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.softwarelivre.gov.br/protocolo-brasilia-1/protocolo-brasilia-1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #2970a6; text-decoration: none;"&gt;http://www.softwarelivre.gov.br/protocolo-brasilia-1/protocolo-brasilia-1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
